<br>
I'd personally like to see some damage associated with a spell like this. Perhaps X points irresistable damage. Where X is equal to the target's(receiver of the buff) current stamina points at the time of impact. If you hit nothing then it'll just end once your stamina runs out.<br>
<br>
 <p>Oanka Lorekeeper/Lydell Lorekeeper <BR>Sacred Guardians <BR>Fennin Ro


</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uxscion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xscion</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/6/01 2:10:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=497.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: an Idea for the Yonder lines or a new line.</span><hr size=1> Hehe, how about an AE buff that made 2H weapons actually hit like they should! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufusionforcewiz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FusionForceWiz</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smokin.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/13/01 7:34:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=497.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://fusionforcewiz.homestead.com/files/FusionBoom.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: an Idea for the Yonder lines or a new line.</span><hr size=1> no damage and no fixing 2hs in this spell.  Well maby the Caster of this spell would take damage if he ran into somthing.<br>
