Or i fighting with this  Ogger Warrior that has just about 2000 more HP than my mana bar has to do damage to him.  I turn away and cast this spell with a /rude.  Ogger cries as his meal goes flyin away from  him. <p><A HREF=http://www.defianteq.com/><IMG border="0" SRC=http://fusionforcewiz.homestead.com/files/Sig2.gif></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufusionforcewiz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FusionForceWiz</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smokin.gif BORDER=0> at: 8/13/01 7:38:58 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=devinetaste>DevineTaste</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 8:35:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=497.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Yonder</span><hr size=1>  I just think they need to make yonder work /sigh. Sick of the 2 feet away ports <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
